83649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"停個人遊無用架<br />\n<br />\nL簽係無限中出的<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=314781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D314781&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=a40e26f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D314781&h=d40cd089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=314781</a><br />\n【新聞極客】內地L簽旅客毋須報團來港 變相自由行旅遊"},{"pid":"3a3b291961308b501c159e48965050e5fe805576","tid":1848394,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:46:23.000Z","msg":"所以封關先有用"},{"pid":"b39d9b400dcf41c0e2ab42f999ab0b96bb248eaf","tid":1848394,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"104c9ed7b5cf6eda535497775eecacb6c5889a97","tid":1848394,"uid":183649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"停個人遊無用架<br />\n<br />\nL簽係無限中出的<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=314781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D314781&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=a40e26f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D314781&h=d40cd089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=314781</a><br />\n【新聞極客】內地L簽旅客毋須報團來港 變相自由行旅遊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"用唔到啦<br />\n冇旅行社"},{"pid":"55c1cc05501d05f499ab1dc528cbeb15a79cc900","tid":1848394,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2ef80e43b876110212af29c87e95485a27c2b94","tid":1848394,"uid":296445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:45:06.000Z","msg":"深圳出張假機票就入到香港啦, 之前CABLE有講過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:49:55.000Z","msg":"原來6年前已經有人咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>內地旅行社代辦假簽證遊港澳</strong><br />\n2014/05/04 15:05<br />\n<br />\n中央電視台揭發深圳及珠海多間旅行社為居民代辦假簽證，協助他們到港澳旅遊。有旅行社職員更教旅客過關時如何避免被識破。<br />\n<br />\n內地收緊港澳個人遊簽證，央視記者到深圳羅湖口岸假裝要到香港，有旅行社稱不用港澳通行證，只要假裝去外國玩，出示一張經香港去外地的機票便可。<br />\n<br />\n旅行社就是利用經香港乘飛機到外地可以在港停留七天的漏洞，替旅客出票。有職員甚至教記者如何在過關時不被識破。<br />\n<br />\n在珠海拱北口岸，同樣有旅行社和商場店舖幫旅客代辦假的外國簽證過澳門。職員還說已有很多人利用這類地下簽證過澳門。<br />\n<br />\n今年第一季珠海各口岸出入境人次高達 2600 萬，創歷來新高，邊檢查獲的假簽證也越來越多。當局指幫人代辦假簽證或利用假簽證出境均會被罰款，同時留有紀錄，影響日後進出港澳。"},{"pid":"5ec2d3dfd9850717ea8bd828007cd44d081b751c","tid":1848394,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b39d9b400dcf41c0e2ab42f999ab0b96bb248eaf","tid":1848394,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"104c9ed7b5cf6eda535497775eecacb6c5889a97","tid":1848394,"uid":183649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"停個人遊無用架<br />\n<br />\nL簽係無限中出的<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=314781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D314781&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=a40e26f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D314781&h=d40cd089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=314781</a><br />\n【新聞極客】內地L簽旅客毋須報團來港 變相自由行旅遊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"用唔到啦<br />\n冇旅行社"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:50:55.000Z","msg":"2017年8月開始 L簽不需要旅行社送關<br />\n可以直接經深圳各口岸入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de71ffd05fd9dd791c0235e11665a74c39b3082","tid":1848394,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:51:27.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"26a